=Yuán Hóngdào 袁宏道 (1568-1610)=
* 字[[中郎]]
* 號[[石公]]
==Literature==
===Translations===
* [[Jonathan Chaves]]: Pilgrim of the Clouds: Poems and Essays by Yüan Hung-tao and His Brothers. New York: Weatherhill, 1978
===PhD Dissertations===
* Ming-shui Hung: Yüan Hung-tao and the Late Ming Literary and Intellectual Movement. University of Wisconsin, 1974
* Martine Vallette-Hémery: Yuan Hongdao (1568-1610): Théorie et pratique littéraires. Paris, 1982
* Chih-p'ing Chou: Yuan Hung-tao (1568-1610) and Trends of Self-expression in Late Ming Literature. Indiana University, 1982
* Herbert Butz: Yüan Hung-tao's "Reglement beim Trinken" (Shang-cheng). University Heidelberg
===Monographs===
* [[任訪秋]]: 袁中郎研究. 上海: 古籍出版社, 1983
* Herbert Butz: Yüan Hung-tao's "Reglement beim Trinken" (Shang-cheng). Heidelberger Schriften zur Ostasienkunde 12, Frankfurt: Haag & Herchen, 1988
* Chih-p'ing Chou: Yüan hung-tao and the Kung-an School. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 1988
